(slaps Josh's back)

00:33:12,958 --> 00:33:15,961
♪♪

00:33:28,473 --> 00:33:31,176
HI, I'M JEFF COHEN, C. E. O.
OF VOYAGE AIR GUITAR.

00:33:31,176 --> 00:33:33,411
I'M HERE WITH MY SON JOSH.
HI.

00:33:33,411 --> 00:33:36,915
AND WE'RE RAISING $500,000
IN THIS ROUND OF FINANCING

00:33:36,915 --> 00:33:38,617
FOR 5% OF THE COMPANY.

00:33:38,617 --> 00:33:40,585
WOW.
(coughs)

00:33:40,585 --> 00:33:44,256
OH! WHOA!
